1. *Kurs* dinara je danas u odnosu na evro stabilan. (*Exchange rate* of dinar is stable today in relation to euro.) 
2. Idem na *kurs* engleskog jezika da bih ga usavršila. (I am going to an *English language course* to improve it.) 
3. Moram da prijavim *kurs* za obuku za posao. (I have to register for a *training course* for work.) 
4. On je već *kursirao* ovaj put, nije želeo da ide peške. (He already *took the route* this time, he didn't want to walk.) 
5. *Kurs* akcija je u stalnom padu već nekoliko nedelja. (*Stock price* has been continuously declining for a few weeks.) 
6. Predavač je bio izvanredan na ovom *kursu*. (The lecturer was outstanding in this *course*.) 
7. *Kurs* jezika u ovoj školi je izuzetno popularan. (*Language course* in this school is extremely popular.) 
8. *Kurs* broda bio je promenjen zbog lošeg vremena. (*Ship's course* was changed due to bad weather.) 
9. Dugo sam se spremala za taj *kurs* i napokon sam položila ispit. (I prepared for that *course* for a long time and finally passed the exam.) 
10. Naša firma je organizovala *kurseve* za usavršavanje zaposlenih. (Our company organized *training courses* for employee development.)